Description_lang: Summons a Demonic Circle for $d. Cast Demonic Circle: Teleport to teleport to its location and remove all movement slowing effects.$?s58081[If you cast Demonic Circle: Summon while controlling an Eye of Kilrogg, the circle will appear where the eye is located.][]
